### Subscription entity HTTP tests
### Subscription 엔티티 관련 API: 가입, 조회, 이체, 해지, 만기 처리

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@adminEmail = hanaro
@adminPassword = 12345678
@userEmail = user1@test.com
@userPassword = 12345678
@newProductAccountNumber = 30100010001

### Admin 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{adminEmail}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("admin_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### User 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{userEmail}}",
  "password": "{{userPassword}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("user_token", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### Subscription 가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "accountNumber": "{{newProductAccountNumber}}"
}

> {%
client.global.set("subscription_id", response.body.data.id);
%}

### Subscription 내 가입 내역 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Subscription 이체
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/transfer
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "subscriptionId": {{subscription_id}},
  "amount": 50000,
  "fromAccountNumber": "12345678901"
}

### Subscription 해지
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/{{subscription_id}}/terminate
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

### Subscription 관리자 회원별 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/2/subscriptions
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Subscription 만기 처리
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/users/maturity
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### Subscription 비정상 테스트: 존재하지 않는 가입 해지
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/user/subscriptions/999999/terminate
Authorization: Bearer {{user_token}}

